title: Hour 2 - Steph Curry's Greatness, Chris Mannix
itunes:title: Hour 2 - Steph Curry's Greatness, Chris Mannix
description:
Dan describes Steph Curry's contribution to the Warriors and the game of basketball. And Chris Mannix gets heated as he and Dan discuss last night's NBA Finals clinching game.
